'''Andrea Robinson''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Singing|singer]] and [[voice acting|voice actress]]. She has been a [[Choir|chorus]] member and singing voice for other actresses in many films ([[animated]] and [[live action]]). Her most prominent job as a singing voice of another actress is Sister Mary Robert ([[Wendy Makkena]]) in ''[[Sister Act]]''. Her most prominent role in animation is the singing voice of [[Characters_of_Disney's_The_Little_Mermaid#Queen_Athena|Queen Athena]] in ''[[The Little Mermaid: Ariel's Beginning]].''
==Filmography/Soundtrack== *''[[Beauty and the Beast: The Enchanted Christmas]]'' (1997) (uncredited) - Chorus *''[[Sister Act 2: Back in the Habit]]'' (1993) (voice) - Sister Mary Robert (singing) *''[[The Princess and the Cobbler]]'' (1993) (voice) - Pop vocalist ("Am I Feeling Love") (re-edited versions) *''[[Sister Act]]'' (1992) (voice) - Sister Mary Robert (singing) *''[[Falcon Crest]]'' - Singer (2 episodes, 1987) *''[[Crazy Moon (film)|Crazy Moon]]'' (1987) - Hearing Impaired Teenager *''[[Yogi's First Christmas]]'' (1980) (TV) (voice) - Singer *''[[American Hot Wax]]'' (1978) - Girls Backstage *''[[The Little Mermaid: Ariel's Beginning]]'' (2008) (performer: "Athena's Song") *''[[The Tigger Movie]]'' (2000) (performer: "Your Heart Will Lead You Home") *''[[MGM Sing-Alongs: Searching for Your Dreams]]'' (1997) (performer: "Now and Forever") *''[[The Pebble and the Penguin]]'' (1995) (performer: "Now and Forever")
